  "text": "PC3 cells was purchased from American Type Culture Collection and maintained in RPMI 1640 medium supplemented with 10% FBS. Cell transfection and the Due-Glo Luciferase Assay System (Promega, Madison, WI) were performed as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
